    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! This car has been so good to me\u2014it's in really wonderful shape and drives super smooth. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, making it perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway. I\u2019m honestly going to miss it, but I\u2019m excited for it to find a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
