    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 atmospheric inline-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a variable M differential lock for superior traction. This example features essential enthusiast-grade maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-driven machine, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, providing an uncompromising analog performance profile.",
