      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54B32 high-pressure 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis benefits from reinforced subframe mounting points and refreshed suspension bushings, ensuring the precision handling this platform is known for. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul and valve adjustment. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain remains robust with excellent compression across all cylinders. A visceral, analog performance machine ready for the tarmac.",
